---
title: Mediterranean Tomato & Silverbeet Risotto with Parmesan & Roasted Almonds
description: Satisfy your tastebuds with an expertly cooked and flavoured risotto (in case it wasn’t clear, you’re the expert!). Hearty and homey, this warming bowl incorporates caramelised cherry tomatoes and silverbeet to create a risotto that has everyone humming from bliss.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
